uct requirements.  Downstream companies can also access the import market easily, at minimal costs.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s8\sl240\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs23\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 There are no import tarrifs charged on many of these products.}}}
